$('#articles').append('<%= j render(@articles) %>')
//instead of always replacing the pagination, lets only replace it if we have page on our @articles result
//if we do, replace the pagination and if we don't completely remove it
<% if @articles.next_page %>
	$('.pagination').replaceWith('<%= j will_paginate(@articles) %>');
<% else %>
	$('.pagination').remove();
<% end %>
<% sleep 1 %>